message: Are you ready to revolutionize how you approach conflict? Learn how different personality types approach conflict and discover strategies to foster resolution with greater ease in our newest Justia Webinar.

From navigating high-stakes negotiations, mediating workplace disputes, or managing challenging client relationships, guest speaker William Stavros will illuminate how the Enneagram personality model can help you build stronger connections and navigate conflict with skill and understanding. Personality as a Conflict Resolution Tool: Exploring the Enneagram Types begins promptly at 2 p.m. ET / 11 a.m. PT on Wednesday, October 23, 2024.
bottomline: Seats are limited, so reserve yours today!

message: As a lawyer, you navigate conflict resolution in many different realms across your practice, from client relations to legal adversaries. What if we told you there was a tool to take the headache out of these situations?

Join us for our latest Justia Webinar where guest speaker William Stavros explores how the Enneagram of Personality can help reveal the best way for you to build stronger connections and navigate conflict in your practice. Personality as a Conflict Resolution Tool: Exploring the Enneagram Types begins promptly at 2 p.m. ET / 11 a.m. PT on Wednesday, October 23, 2024.
